structure.unit: SALES OF REALTY OF PERSONS UNDER DISABILITY (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 277, sec. 21, effective July 15, 1982. -- Transferred 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 84, sec. 1, effective July 1, 1953, from C.C. sec. 497. -- C.C. sec. 497 repealed, reenacted, and amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 137, sec. 3.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Lien to secure payment of proceeds -- Collection of interest and proceeds -- Purchaser may pay amount due into court.
metadata.note: . 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396, sec. 115 would have amended this section effective July 1, 1982. However, 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396 was repealed by 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 146, also effective July 1, 1982.
